description.description: Detailed description of the Steps, optional

status.description: The specified status. When this property is not configured, the current of Steps would be used to automatically specify the state; if the prop does not match the state specified by current, the automatically matched state would be overwritten.
status.description_zh: 指定的状态。如果未配置此属性，则 Steps 的当前将用于自动指定状态;如果 prop 与 current 指定的状态不匹配，则自动匹配的状态将被覆盖。
